{"id":991,"date":"2024-02-27T07:01:37","date_gmt":"2019-11-27T01:31:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/a-glamorous-retreat-dressing-room-design-ideas-to-feel-gorgeous-everyday\/"},"modified":"2023-09-05T17:22:35","modified_gmt":"2023-09-05T11:52:35","slug":"latest-dressing-room-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/latest-dressing-room-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"A Glamorous Retreat: Dressing Room Design Ideas To Feel Gorgeous Everyday"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>These chic and functional dressing room design are just what you need to prepare for an evening out.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2018Mirror, mirror on the wall, who is the fairest of them all?\u2019 As the evil queen from Snow White was to learn, it barely matters who is the fairest of them all. Instead, a gentle heart is what made Snow White superior to the beautiful queen. Helping you find your beauty and create a space where you can relax is our guide on the latest dressing room ideas. We have something for everyone \u2013 those with walk-in closets that can double up as dressing rooms, those with tiny bedrooms with barely any space to move to those who are looking for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wardrobe-design-dressing-table-mirror\/\">wardrobe designs with dressing table<\/a>. Our fantastic set of dressing room designs and ideas will set you well on your way.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Simple Scandinavian Style<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This Scandinavian inspired dressing room design with its elegant lines and pristine finish is surely every woman\u2019s dream come true. This type of dressing room furniture is a mix of closed storage, drawers and open shelves providing oodles of wardrobe space. A handsome dressing table with a simple cabinet design is set to the side. The central floor area is left open and clutter-free enhancing the minimalist yet stylish feel that the dressing room has. The soft ambient light is complemented by discrete task lights around the dresser, finishing the room\u2019s look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055710\/simple-scandinavian-style-for-dressing-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"Simple scandinavian style dressing room design with its elegant lines and its type of dressing room furniture\" class=\"wp-image-2109\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A pristine and elegant dressing room provides the perfect stage for you to shine<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Waste Not, Want Not<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Space is like gold for an interior designer and it is sheer blasphemy to waste it or not utilise it properly. Precious real estate has been used to the fullest in this wardrobe design with dressing table. Note the clever use of a narrow space between the door and window. A single door wardrobe has been installed along with a mirrored dressing table. Drawers run the length of the dressing cupboard. And that is not all! There is storage space built behind the mirror, giving the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/small-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">small bedroom<\/a> that extra advantage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055709\/mirror-to-utilise-every-inch-of-space-for-dressing-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"Dressing room design for bedroom with storage space built behind mirror, its kind of dressing cupboard\" class=\"wp-image-2110\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hide storage behind the mirror to utilise every inch of space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tuck It Tight Into An Alcove<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We firmly believe that space constraints need not dampen your enthusiasm for classy d\u00e9cor. This dressing room design illustrates just that. The small alcove is effectively converted into a dressing room mirror. The dressing cabinet design is quite smart, with the set of drawers mounted on the wall, leaving the floor space empty. Open shelves add to the clean look and a full-length mirror makes dressing easy and convenient. The entire space seems even bigger with a mirror running alongside seemingly doubling its size.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055708\/stylish-dressing-room-design-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Dressing cabinet design is quite smart, with set of drawers mounted on the wall to make stylish dressing room design\" class=\"wp-image-2111\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Convert a narrow alcove into a practical but stylish dressing room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Reflections That Won\u2019t Be In Vain<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our next recommendation for dressing room designs with mirrors is a gorgeous walk in closet. The wall of open shelves filled with shoes, that will make even Imelda Marcos envious, sure grabs your attention. What is also striking is the floor to ceiling mirror that makes this narrow space seem much bigger. Closer inspection will reveal that the mirror is mounted on a sliding wardrobe door making it a wonderful cupboard design for dressing room. The other dressing room furniture is a whimsical rocking chair that adds a lovely pop of colour, and a set of sleek drawers. This dressing room has everything you need to help you get ready for the day or prepare to dazzle at the party.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055706\/mirrors-on-sliding-wardrobe-doors-for-dressing-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"Wardrobe design with dressing table with mirrors on sliding wardrobe doors serve several functional purposes and look classy to boot\" class=\"wp-image-2112\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Mirrors on sliding wardrobe doors serve several functional purposes and look classy to boot<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lights Make Your Dressing Room Pretty<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While you can always install task lighting to aid your dressing, there is nothing quite like natural light to do the job. This wardrobe design with dressing table does exactly that by taking full advantage of light streaming in through the balcony glass doors. One-fourth of the wardrobe is given over to the dresser with a mirror being installed on the door. Discreet drawers are built below ensuring a clean look that is also practical. Flush mount ceiling light right above provides the required light for gloomy days and dressing after daylight hours.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055705\/dressing-room-lighting-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Dressing design to install task lighting to aid your dressing, its one of best dressing room idea\" class=\"wp-image-2113\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The placement of the dressing cabinet section of the wardrobe makes all the difference<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get That Seating Right<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A good wardrobe with dressing table design will give you practical storage solution and a mirror. A great dressing cabinet design also provides seating. The seating in this dressing area is solved by unconventional means, through a pouf. The pouf can magically blend into the wardrobe by being tucked away under the mirror in the space specially designed for this purpose. When required, simply pull it out and convert the area into a mini dressing room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055704\/wardrobe-with-dressing-table-design.jpg\" alt=\"Wardrobe with dressing table design will give you practical storage solution and a mirror\" class=\"wp-image-2114\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Say poof and the pouf conveniently disappears<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Slim It Down<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This small bedroom has a dressing cabinet design that floors you. Side tables are entirely done away with and instead a dressing cabinet is placed. In keeping with the dimensions of the space, the dressing cabinet and mirror are kept quite slim. The drawers are small but provide enough storage space. The mirror is purposely designed to be tall and narrow to add height to the room. Note how there is empty space left around the dressing cabinet, adding to the open feel of the room. Placing the mirror next to the window also makes for a great dressing room idea.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055701\/dressing-room-mirror-design-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Dressing cabinet design for small bedroom to keeping with the dimensions of the space, dressing cabinet and mirror\" class=\"wp-image-2117\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Go slim and tall when space is a premium<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want a dressing room that makes yoru feel gorgeous every day\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/09111527\/want-a-dressing-room-that-makes-yoru-feel-gorgeous-every-day.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Integrate The Dressing Cabinet<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make your furniture multi-task with this dressing design. A workspace, a TV panel and a dressing cabinet come together to create a fabulous combo. The dressing cabinet is simple in its elegance with the mirrored closet doing double duty as a cupboard and a mirror.&nbsp; A floating shelf is a conveniently located flat surface to hold your make-up while you get your mascara on right. An ottoman in the same neutral shade as the rest of the room is a good seating option, while a pair of slim pendants provide task lighting above the mirror.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055700\/dressing-cabinet-for-dressing-room-design-1.jpg\" alt=\"Dressing room furniture with a workspace, a tv panel and a dressing cabinet come together to create a fabulous combo\" class=\"wp-image-2116\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Seamlessly blend the dressing cabinet with the rest of the room for a smooth finish<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wardrobe-design-for-bedroom\/\">Latest wardrobe designs for your bedroom in 2020<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Add Class With Glass<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for dressing room wardrobe design ideas that are awe-inspiring? Here is one that will get your creative juices flowing. Don\u2019t shut away your closet contents behind plain-vanilla dressing cupboard with closed storage. They may hide many a messy sin but don\u2019t hold a patch to glass doors. This dressing cupboard has many intelligent organising solutions to ensure the contents of the wardrobe appear neat and worthy of display. Concealed lights shed subtle light on clothes and accessories helping you easily locate your things. Not to forget it gives your dressing room a sense of wow.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055659\/closets-with-glass-doors-for-dressing-room.jpg\" alt=\"Dressing room wardrobe design with glass doors spell luxury, class and style \" class=\"wp-image-2118\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Closets with glass doors spell luxury, class and style<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"2971\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/05171834\/best-colours-for-dressing-room.jpg\" alt=\"Best colours for a dressing room are grey, black, brown, white and wood tone\" class=\"wp-image-49190\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/05171834\/best-colours-for-dressing-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/05171834\/best-colours-for-dressing-room-95x300.jpg 95w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/05171834\/best-colours-for-dressing-room-324x1024.jpg 324w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/05171834\/best-colours-for-dressing-room-768x2427.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/05171834\/best-colours-for-dressing-room-486x1536.jpg 486w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/05171834\/best-colours-for-dressing-room-648x2048.jpg 648w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/05171834\/best-colours-for-dressing-room-150x474.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">When Your Dressing Cabinet Is Not A Cabinet<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who says that a dressing design needs an entire plethora of cabinets, wardrobes and racks to be complete? The absolute simplicity of this dressing design proves that all you need is some imagination. Several floating shelves flank a full-length mirror in an aesthetically pleasing pattern. These are handy for keeping perfumes, make-up and jewellery. Dark tones of the mirror frame and the shelves offset paler tones of colour in the room. The dressing design is highly recommended if you want to save on floor space and have a wall to spare.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055658\/clever-design-with-shelves-flanking-mirror-for-dressing-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"dressing room design ideas in bedroom \" class=\"wp-image-2119\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An easy to install and clever design with shelves flanking a mirror<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make Lofty Ideas A Reality<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are times when a wardrobe design with dressing table means that you must cut down on loft space. Not with this space-saving solution. The cupboards in this room begin with a dressing cabinet. Drawers finished with wood and ivory alternate below a deep-set mirror. The top of the drawer closet holds dresser items. The loft stretches above the dresser and across the room. This design element above the dressing table does not compromise on space. Since the dressing cabinet section of this wardrobe is next to the door, the open space is one of the first things that greets you instead of a boring cupboard.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17055657\/spare-storage-space-for-dressing-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"In bedroom, dressing room interior designs \" class=\"wp-image-2120\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A convenient and practical design for those who want their mirror and their spare storage space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There you have it! A bunch of beautiful dressing room design ideas where luxury meets practicality. Needless to different designs will suit different individuals depending on lifestyle and priorities. However, these design ideas are sure to give your home an everlasting element of style and class.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n                <option 